🔹 1. Create Hierarchy (Product → Category → Sub-Category)
In Data pane (left side):
Find:
Category
Sub-Category
Product Name
Right-click Category → Create Hierarchy
Name it: Product Hierarchy
Drag:
Sub-Category into Category
Product Name under Sub-Category

✅ Done hierarchy

🔹 2. Location Hierarchy (Country → State → City → Postal Code)
Right-click Country → Create Hierarchy
Name: Location Hierarchy
Drag in order:
State
City
Postal Code
